{"tid":1973544,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[排支運動] 北京大外宣踢鐵板 法國外長召見中國大使表達不滿","createTime":"2020-04-15T08:53:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T09:02:33.000Z","uid":224066,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"773df3bbc8af5914ee0988e788befee37a7ba8aa","tid":1973544,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgcdn.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20200415/4760x3171_941933365499.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgcdn.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F1024%2F20200415%2F4760x3171_941933365499.jpg&h=a7697200&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國駐法大使館企圖在法國推動大外宣，誇耀中國抗疫模式並批評西方國家處理不當。法國外長勒德里安今日召見中華人民共和國駐法大使盧沙野，以表達對中國近日相關言行的不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgcdn.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20200415/6960x4667_80151502181.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgcdn.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F1024%2F20200415%2F6960x4667_80151502181.jpg&h=f5f6dec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n勒德里安（Jean-Yves Le Drian）在新聞稿中首先提及自2019冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19，武漢肺炎）疫情12月開始後，「中法兩國保持互助，包括兩國間相互運送防疫物資」。然而，「中國駐法大使近日公開場合的立場，並不符合兩國良好的雙邊關係」。<br />\n<br />\n勒德里安表示，「我在召見時，清楚傳達我對中國駐法大使近日言行的不贊同」。根據法媒表示，所指言行與中國大使館透過宣傳手段，誇耀中國政府抗疫「勝利」，同時批評西方國家危機治理有關。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中國大使館12日於官網張貼一篇名為「把顛倒的事實再顛倒過來 &mdash;&mdash;一名中國駐法國使館外交官對新冠肺炎疫情的觀察」的文章。文中批評西方國家抹黑中國，並毫無根據的指控法國「養老院護理人員擅離職守，集體逃離，導致老人成批餓死、病死」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EVd4EvMWoAENSBV?format=jpg&amp;name=360x360\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEVd4EvMWoAENSBV%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3D360x360&h=b6351968&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此文引發許多議論，策略研究基金會（FRS）研究員與巴黎政治學院（Sciences Po）教授波恩達茲（Antoine Bondaz）便表示，「中國大使館的這篇文章，又再一次丟盡顏面。謠言、不實資訊、侮辱全都有。不反應、不譴責，就是放任一個大使可以胡作非為，連一點尊重都沒有」。<br />\n<br />\n對於外長召見盧沙野一事，無國界記者組織法國總部主席Pierre Haski（韓石）表示贊同。他在推特上表示：「這是期待中的，也是必須的。外長勒德里安因中國張貼令人無法容忍的文章後召見大使。大使館的推特現在變得可親多了。」"},{"pid":"e6b7ff9446ba21bff0736957b4d57609d522fb64","tid":1973544,"uid":45914,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:54:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c54b6db04435c2ef4ff7088a46da6b699c43dfb0","tid":1973544,"uid":57674,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:57:54.000Z","msg":"又俾人貼堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3ba27597445976c857d826d674c7c54e72c24fb","tid":1973544,"uid":123738,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:59:00.000Z","msg":"支那一定會派軍坦平巴黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4d4d2c0fd92c1d186474d106b403eae99d99579","tid":1973544,"uid":192754,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:59:22.000Z","msg":"Nmsl"},{"pid":"412a907789c4c147b766a76028195714499189f0","tid":1973544,"uid":164043,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T08:59:57.000Z","msg":"Cnmbnese"},{"pid":"de0878c14c5cc738ef3dc355f291d86bd5d7e26e","tid":1973544,"uid":51039,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:01:20.000Z","msg":"大外宣加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n靠你地喇"},{"pid":"c5831694f550d73645e67b6c1e9c7dc4854749f9","tid":1973544,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:02:33.000Z","msg":"馬克龍繼續奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}